      "raw_text": "INDIANAPOLIS. Feb. 2. - The\nwage conference between the miners\nand operators is being held today be-\nhind closed doors. Each side Is COM\nbative. President Mitchell has given\nan ultimatum to the operators, saying\nthat the eighthour day has been set\ntied upon by the mine workers and\nthat no bituminous miner will ever\nwork longer day 1t will be sur\nprising If an agreement is reached\nwithin a week."
